marketing: Shell Spirax S6 GXME Ultra 75W-80 is a unique fuel-efficient, long-life gear oil designed to give the ultimate in performance and protection to meet the requirements of current and future heavy duty gearboxes. Specially formulated fully synthetic base oils plus a unique new additive technology give improved lubrication and longer life for your equipment.
